This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to extract quantitative information from web data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
